e proportion of Saint Lucia versus the United States - or Jamaica.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David-and-Goliath\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\"}, {\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999996275221986, \"rank\": 3.723845877528998e-07, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}, {\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999867472981, \"rank\": 1.272871801837499e-08, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the proportion\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"the United States\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saint Lucia, an Eastern Caribbean island nation, had never previously had an athlete on the Olympic podium while Americans have won well over 300 titles in athletics alone, topping the all-time medal table by a massive margin.\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999996275221986, \"rank\": 3.723845877528998e-07, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Eastern Caribbean island nation\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic podium\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1349}, {